OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,FA Houthi official threatened the UK
OL,7,Fand US in one of the first in-depth
OL,8,Finterviews the Yemen-based, Iran-
OL,9,Fbacked group has given since the Gaza
OL,10,Fwar, as Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,11,FKachroo reports.
OL,13,FThe Houthis have vowed to continue
OL,14,Fattacks on UK and US ships in the Red
OL,15,FSea if there is no ceasefire in Gaza,
OL,16,Fand told ITV News it would attack the
OL,17,FUK itself if it had the capacity to do
OL,18,Fso.
