OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,FIn the first in-depth interview given
OL,7,Fto Western media by the Iranian-backed
OL,8,FYemeni group since the October 7 Hamas
OL,9,Fattacks in Israel, a Houthi official
OL,10,Fsaid it will target the UK and the US
OL,11,F"wherever" it can reach.
OL,13,F"If we had rockets and warplanes that
OL,14,Fcould reach deep into America and
OL,15,FBritain, we would hit them without any
OL,16,Fhesitation, as long as they are
OL,17,Fattacking Yemen", Mohammed al-Bukhaiti
OL,18,F- a spokesperson and official - told
OL,19,FITV News Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,20,FKachroo.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
