OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,F"This is a legitimate right for
OL,7,FYemen", he added.
OL,9,F'If we had rockets and warplanes that
OL,10,Fcould reach deep into the US and UK,
OL,11,Fof course we would hit them', Houthi
OL,12,Fofficial Mohammad al-Bukhaiti told ITV
OL,13,FNews Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,14,FKachroo.
OL,16,FThe Houthi official said the group
OL,17,Fwould escalate if Israeli action in
OL,18,FGaza continues with what it perceives
OL,19,Fas Western support.
