OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,FHe said that if aggression against
OL,7,FGaza does not stop and if the "siege
OL,8,Fis not lifted" there will be an
OL,9,F"escalation" which will be "announced
OL,10,Fin due course", Mr al-Bukhaiti said.
OL,11,FHe added that the Houthis have "many
OL,12,Foptions" in terms of escalation, if
OL,13,Fthe UK and US were to "target Yemeni
OL,14,Fcivilians".
OL,16,F"Our war (attacks against US and UK
OL,17,Fvessels) is a legitimate one", he
OL,18,Fsaid, speaking from within Yemen.
