OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,F"We did not initiate attacks on
OL,7,FAmerica or Britain either in the Red
OL,8,FSea or in their countries, but if
OL,9,Fthere is aggression against us from
OL,10,Fany country we will respond wherever
OL,11,Four hands can reach", he added.
OL,13,FMr al-Bukhaiti didn't rule out
OL,14,Ftargeting British and American
OL,15,Fembassies and army bases, when asked
OL,16,Fby ITV News.
