OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,F"Such operations are not on the table
OL,7,Fnow but we have many options to
OL,8,Fescalate if there is American and
OL,9,FBritish escalation that targets Yemeni
OL,10,Fcivilians", the Houthi official said.
OL,12,FRohit Kachroo questioned Mohammed al-
OL,13,FBukahiti on whether the Houthis were
OL,14,Fusing the situation in Gaza to broaden
OL,15,Fsupport in Yemen.
OL,17,FThe Houthis are a Shia Islamist
OL,18,Fpolitical and military group - backed
OL,19,Fby Iran - that has been fighting a war
OL,20,Fagainst Yemen's government - which is
OL,21,Fsupported by Saudi Arabia - since 2014.
