OL,3,CHouthis threaten UK and US in rare
OL,4,Cinterview with Western media
OL,6,FThe first Houthi attack on commercial
OL,7,Fships in the Red Sea came on 19th
OL,8,FNovember. The group has since attacked
OL,9,Fmore than 20 ships using missiles and
OL,10,Fdrones. The attacks have been in
OL,11,Fresponse to the war in Gaza.
OL,13,FThe Houthis have said they will target
OL,14,Fall ships bound for Israel or vessels
OL,15,Fthat are Israeli-owned or flagged. UK
OL,16,Fand US-flagged and owned ships have
OL,17,Falso been targeted.
